reviewText: When we got it found out you have to be in another country to watch. It is setup for region 2 DVD player not the same as us players I can either spend $ 60 and get different dvd player to watch $ 5 movie on or put on shelf and never watch
My son loves this dvd and it arrived sooner than expected.
This video sucks it's not allowed in this country, and the seller won't take it back. So it's pretty dumb that I spent money for something I can't watch,
